{"ID":"20220711194702-fzu0l2i","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220711194702-fzu0l2i","title":"SpringBoot","type":"doc","updated":"20221020201934"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220711201100-p1235wu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220711201100-p1235wu","updated":"20220711201159"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SpringBoot概念"}]},{"ID":"20220711194702-s1t40lu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220711194702-s1t40lu","updated":"20220711200450"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为什么需要SpringBoot？​"}]},{"ID":"20220711200452-zjpe9f4","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220711200452-zjpe9f4","updated":"20220711200544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220711200454-abqyuoy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711200454-abqyuoy","updated":"20220711200523"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为Spring、SpringMVC需要使用大量的配置文件（xml文件）"}]},{"ID":"20220711200526-exyq9t4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711200526-exyq9t4","updated":"20220711200544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"还需要配置各种对象，把使用的对象放入到spring容器中才能使用对象"}]}]},{"ID":"20220711200552-irtmgpl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220711200552-irtmgpl","updated":"20220711200605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"SpringBoot作用"}]},{"ID":"20220711200610-c4otdhm","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220711200610-c4otdhm","updated":"20220711200658"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220711200611-tbqti3h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711200611-tbqti3h","updated":"20220711200645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SpringBoot就相当于不需要配置文件的Spring+SpringMVC，常用的框架和第三方库都已经配置好了，拿来就可以用"}]},{"ID":"20220711200646-hk7rqvh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711200646-hk7rqvh","updated":"20220711200658"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"开发效率很高，使用方便"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712095241-8aodbzn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220712095241-8aodbzn","updated":"20220713182355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一章 xml和JavaConfig"}]},{"ID":"20220711201053-h5r1pme","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220711201053-h5r1pme","updated":"20220711201123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaConfig概念"}]},{"ID":"20220711201206-sy99yqq","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220711201206-sy99yqq","updated":"20220711201304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220711201211-ktufwi0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711201211-ktufwi0","updated":"20220711201304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"JavaConfig：使用java类作为xml配置文件的替代，是配置Spring容器的纯java方式，在这个java类中可以穿件java对象，把对象放入spring容器中（注入到容器）"}]}]},{"ID":"20220711201328-t8bex2m","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220711201328-t8bex2m","updated":"20220711210950"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例子：使用springboot简化配置"}]},{"ID":"20220711210953-xjkgwxd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711210953-xjkgwxd","updated":"20220711211009"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"学生类"}]},{"ID":"20220711210955-ryuw0ta","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220711210955-ryuw0ta"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.vo;\n\npublic class Student {\n    private String name;\n    public Integer age;\n    private String sex;\n\n    public String getName() {\n        return name;\n    }\n\n    public void setName(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n\n    public Integer getAge() {\n        return age;\n    }\n\n    public void setAge(Integer age) {\n        this.age = age;\n    }\n\n    public String getSex() {\n        return sex;\n    }\n\n    public void setSex(String sex) {\n        this.sex = sex;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public String toString() {\n        return \"Student{\" +\n                \"name='\" + name + '\\'' +\n                \", age=\" + age +\n                \", sex='\" + sex + '\\'' +\n                '}';\n    }\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220711210909-uxrxesg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711210909-uxrxesg","updated":"20220711211532"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"SpringConfig配置"}]},{"ID":"20220712084557-h56n6q9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220712084557-h56n6q9","updated":"20220712084557"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@Configuration"}]},{"ID":"20220712084610-c17ei34","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220712084610-c17ei34","updated":"20220712084611"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@Bean"}]},{"ID":"20220711201336-272bfrv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711201336-272bfrv","updated":"20220712094854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"@Configuration："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"放在一个类的上面，表示这个注解下的当前类是做为配置文件使用的，此时被注解的类就相当于beans.xml文件"}]},{"ID":"20220711201339-ibitc3s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711201339-ibitc3s","updated":"20220712094857"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"@Bean："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明对象，把对象注入到容器中"}]},{"ID":"20220711211528-yigbfuq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220711211528-yigbfuq"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"package com.Xia.config;\nimport com.Xia.vo.Student;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;\nimport org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;\n\n\n/**\n * Configuration:表示当前类是作为配置文件使用的木九十用来配置容器的\n *      位置：在类的上面\n *\n *      SpringConfig这个类就相当于beans.xml\n */\n@Configuration\npublic class SpringConfig {\n\n    /**\n     * 创建方法：方法的返回值是  对象  ，在方法的上面加入@Bean\n     * 方法的返回值对象就注入到容器中\n     *\n     * @Bean：把对象注入到Spring容器中，作用相当于\u003cbean\u003e\n     *\n     * 说明：@Bean不指定对象的名称，默认方法名是id\n     *\n     *\n     */\n    @Bean\n    public Student createStudent(){\n        Student s1 = new Student();\n        s1.setName(\"张三\");\n        s1.setAge(20);\n        s1.setSex(\"男\");\n        return s1;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * 指定对象在容器中的名称（指定\u003cbean\u003e的id属性））\n     * @Bean的name属性，指定对象的名称（id）\n     */\n    @Bean(name=\"xthStudent\")\n    public Student makeStudent(){\n        Student s2 = new Student();\n        s2.setName(\"李四\");\n        s2.setAge(22);\n        s2.setSex(\"男\");\n        return s2;\n    }\n\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220711210910-jwby7vx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711210910-jwby7vx","updated":"20220711211547"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"测试类"}]},{"ID":"20220711210910-fp39rsa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711210910-fp39rsa","updated":"20220711211503"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220711211503-whclu1c.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220711201323-dgw7edx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220711201323-dgw7edx"}},{"ID":"20220711201146-dijuvex","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220711201146-dijuvex","updated":"20220712084653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@ImportResource"}]},{"ID":"20220712084633-1qqmyxu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712084633-1qqmyxu","updated":"20220712094849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"@ImportResource："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作用是导入其他的xml配置文件，等于在xml中输入一下格式："}]},{"ID":"20220712084821-iji2xp2","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220712084821-iji2xp2","updated":"20220712091218"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003cimport resources\u003e='其他配置文件'/\u003e\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220712084850-63oqxky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712084850-63oqxky","updated":"20220712090923"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.在配置类中导入xml文件位置"}]},{"ID":"20220712091223-9uzwlmm","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220712091223-9uzwlmm","updated":"20220712091342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"//也可以输入多个配置文件\n@ImportResource(value = \"classpath:applicationContext.xml\",\"classpath:beans.xml\")\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220712090923-oqrg2br","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712090923-oqrg2br","updated":"20220712090924"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712090924-itike72.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712090929-sa5594h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712090929-sa5594h","updated":"20220712091123"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.使用容器中的id"}]},{"ID":"20220712091104-cdtuqm3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091104-cdtuqm3","updated":"20220712091105"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712091105-a1strhk.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712091435-hcmbnf5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220712091435-hcmbnf5","updated":"20220712091445"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@PropertyResource"}]},{"ID":"20220712094807-ig1yler","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220712094807-ig1yler","updated":"20220712094807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"@ComponentScan"}]},{"ID":"20220712091451-nw5kehj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091451-nw5kehj","updated":"20220712094836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"​@PropertyResource："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是读取properties属性配置文件，使用属性配置文件可以实现外部化配置，在程序代码之外提供数据"}]},{"ID":"20220712094704-3v5zaf4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094704-3v5zaf4","updated":"20220712094821"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"@ComponentScan："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为Tiger是注解生成的，所以要用ComponentScan扫描Tiger类的组件"}]},{"ID":"20220712091833-4sm322d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091833-4sm322d","updated":"20220712091835"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"步骤："}]},{"ID":"20220712091836-sog3qda","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091836-sog3qda","updated":"20220712091904"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.在resources目录下，创建properties文件，使用k=v的格式提供数据"}]},{"ID":"20220712094428-yzw1qqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094428-yzw1qqm","updated":"20220712094428"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712094428-05vhyyg.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712091904-7mzkeva","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091904-7mzkeva","updated":"20220712091949"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.在PropertyResource指定properties文件的位置"}]},{"ID":"20220712094502-3ypcgia","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094502-3ypcgia","updated":"20220712094502"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712094502-fk9urtm.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712091949-wih8a93","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712091949-wih8a93","updated":"20220712124029"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"@Value（value=\u0026quot;${key}\u0026quot;）"}]},{"ID":"20220712094529-fc56kk8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094529-fc56kk8","updated":"20220712094530"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712094530-77wecnc.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712094604-jtrduey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094604-jtrduey","updated":"20220712094606"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.测试"}]},{"ID":"20220712094606-p0ss7bp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094606-p0ss7bp","updated":"20220712094623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712094623-xavtkbi.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712094534-gr9d4w5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094534-gr9d4w5","updated":"20220712094535"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原来是全部写在xml文件中的，现在只需要全部写在@Configuration 下即可："}]},{"ID":"20220712094541-1to4abk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094541-1to4abk","updated":"20220712094541"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20220712094337-wngl4rf.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712093629-vf8p2k1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220712093629-vf8p2k1","updated":"20220713182336"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二章 SpringBoot入门"}]},{"ID":"20220712094103-a9sa74n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712094103-a9sa74n","updated":"20220712095422"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SpringBoot是Spring中的一个成员，可以简化Spring，SpringMVC的使用，他的核心还是IOC容器"}]},{"ID":"20220712094338-r6x2plt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220712094338-r6x2plt","updated":"20220712103922"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"特点"}]},{"ID":"20220712103925-127xk0w","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220712103925-127xk0w","updated":"20220825090238"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220712103929-5jurms6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712103929-5jurms6","updated":"20220712103937"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.创建spring应用"}]},{"ID":"20220712103937-dkmo5up","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712103937-dkmo5up","updated":"20220712104004"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.内嵌的tomcat，jetty，Undertow"}]},{"ID":"20220712104004-t3r76ou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104004-t3r76ou","updated":"20220825090238"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.提供了starter起步依赖，简化应用的配置"}]},{"ID":"20220712104036-qesorhf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104036-qesorhf","updated":"20220712104115"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如使用Mybatis框架，需要在Spring项目中，配置MyBatis的对象SqlSessionFactory，Dao的代理对象"}]},{"ID":"20220712104116-2n3xp0r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104116-2n3xp0r","updated":"20220712104152"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在SpringBoot项目中，在pom.xml里加入一个mybatis-spring-boot-starter依赖即可"}]},{"ID":"20220712104152-3v0vwe5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104152-3v0vwe5","updated":"20220712104319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.尽可能去配置spring和第三方库，叫做自动配置（就是把spring中的第三方库中的对象都创建好，放到容器中，开发人员可以直接使用）"}]},{"ID":"20220712104243-yd76m84","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104243-yd76m84","updated":"20220712104321"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.提供了健康检查，统计，外部化配置"}]},{"ID":"20220712104255-xgabn66","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712104255-xgabn66","updated":"20220712104344"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.不用生成代码，不用使用xml做配置"}]}]},{"ID":"20220712103918-tfmshop","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220712103918-tfmshop","updated":"20220712143854"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用SpringBoot（国内地址）提供的初始化器创建项目"}]},{"ID":"20220712133813-558guwv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220712133813-558guwv","updated":"20220712133822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（需联网）"}]},{"ID":"20220712133141-bqc5xax","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220712133141-bqc5xax","updated":"20220712133200"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220712133146-44dbk3t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220